# LMDB tier (T4) — structure (documentation)

Binary LMDB environment path (default): `~/.udos/vectors.lmdb`

Logical stores (see uDosDev UDOS_FIVE_TIER_DATABASE_STRATEGY_LOCKED_v1.md):

- `vector:{uuid}` → float32 embedding bytes
- `meta:{uuid}` → JSON metadata (voxel_id, cell_index, content_hash, tags)
- `sync:{lamport}:{uuid}` → CRDT operation payload (implementation-specific)

HNSW (or IVF) index lives in process memory or companion file — not inside LMDB keys above.

This file is documentation only; the on-disk LMDB is created by the vector runtime.
